{"source_id":"W703","platform":"RSS","author":"Automaton (RSS)","account_type":"メディア","text":"大人気ネズミアニメ殺戮FPS『MOUSE：やとわれの探偵』、発売1か月足らずで「売上約34億円」に。投資費用はすでに全額回収済み\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://automaton-media.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/20260512-442469-header.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></p>PlaySideは5月6日、『MOUSE：やとわれの探偵』が、販売から1か月足らずで販売本数73万本、売上高約34億円を達成したことを、投資家向け情報の中で公表した。","url":"https://automaton-media.com/articles/newsjp/20260512-442469/","timestamp":"2026-05-12T03:29:21Z","extra":{"source_priority":"high","source_genre":"games","source_type":"メディア"}}
